headline: 3 Reasons AFL is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since January 2025, Aflac has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 1.9% while floating around $102.89. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 4.3% gain during that period.
